OL,3,CLondon's crumbling hospitals to
OL,4,Cbenefit from government funding
OL,6,FThe government has revealed which of
OL,7,FLondon's crumbling hospitals will be
OL,8,Frebuilt and when.
OL,10,FBoris Johnson announced the building
OL,11,Fprogramme when he was Prime Minister -
OL,12,Fand Labour agreed to review it. This
OL,13,Fafternoon, Health Secretary Wes
OL,14,FStreeting layed out the Government's
OL,15,Fnew plan.
OL,17,FThe new hospital programme will be
OL,18,Fimplemented in three 'waves' between
OL,19,Fnow and 2039.
