OL,3,CLondon's crumbling hospitals to
OL,4,Cbenefit from government funding
OL,6,FThe first wave will begin between 2025
OL,7,Fand 2030 and includes Frimley Park
OL,8,FHospital and Hillingdon Hospital.
OL,10,FHospitals in the second wave are the
OL,11,FSpecialist Emergency Care Hospital in
OL,12,FSutton, Whipps Cross University
OL,13,FHospital, Princess Alexandra Hospital
OL,14,Fand Watford General - they will begin
OL,15,Fconstruction between 2030 and 2035.
OL,17,FThe third wave will start between 3035
OL,18,Fand 2039 and includes St Mary's
OL,19,FHospital, and Charing Cross and
OL,20,FHammersmith hospitals.
