OL,3,CLondon's crumbling hospitals to
OL,4,Cbenefit from government funding
OL,6,FWes Streeting, from Redbridge, accused
OL,7,Fthe Conservatives of failing to fund
OL,8,Ftheir government's 2019 promise of
OL,9,Fproviding the new facilities by 2030,
OL,10,Fsaying the pledge had been "built on
OL,11,Fthe shaky foundation of false hope".
OL,13,FMr Streeting said the new timetable
OL,14,Fwas "honest, funded and can actually
OL,15,Fbe delivered. It is a serious,
OL,16,Fcredible plan to build the hospitals
OL,17,Four NHS needs."
