OL,3,CLondon's crumbling hospitals to
OL,4,Cbenefit from government funding
OL,6,FPromising that all the new units would
OL,7,Fbe delivered, Mr Streeting said he had
OL,8,Fsecured investment averaging #3
OL,9,Fbillion a year, which he described as
OL,10,Fpart of the largest capital investment
OL,11,Fin the NHS since the previous Labour
OL,12,Fgovernment.
OL,14,FHe also announced a new framework for
OL,15,Fcontracting out construction of the
OL,16,Fnew hospitals, saying this would
OL,17,Fensure the new facilities were
OL,18,Fdelivered "as quickly as possible".
